Sonia sees a white rabbit running through walmart... but what is it doing there of all places...?
Coming June 15th, experience a thrilling and erotic story starring Bartleby Montclair of Dresdin, his boyfriend Sonic the hedgehog, and Sonic's sibs as they travel through Wonderland in an attempt to get home!
